body_html:
I had the same issue, turned out I still had protobuf installed in my path with brew.
Should try to get the version of protobuf in the path with:

protoc -v

if version < 3 then brew uninstall protobuf

body:
I had the same issue, turned out I still had `protobuf` installed in my path with brew. 
Should try to get the version of protobuf in the path with:

`protoc -v`

if version < 3 then `brew uninstall protobuf`
